{"tid":994974,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗喜利二樓開咗間夾公仔（台灣用語慎入","createTime":"2019-01-25T05:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T14:58:17.000Z","uid":1557,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3a20057388cb65b5015217739c46d3b234482208","tid":994974,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:58:25.000Z","msg":"唔知開咗幾耐，最近先發現<br />\n有冇巴打夾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋪仔細細計埋門口位嗰兩部機都係得五部<br />\n逼撚到仆街<br />\n個夾力度好夠，不過防甩片算緊，頓甩（前後落夾）有一半機唔用得，只能靠多段甩（前後前後前後前落夾）做啲啲甩幅<br />\n個人嚟講覺得出貨都幾需要技術，特別係正版盒裝公仔<br />\n<br />\n喺香港嚟講夾公仔比起台灣賺嘅機會細啲，因為距離保夾次數少過台灣好多，所以基本上都淨係可以當興趣夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以分享下香港有咩地方有夾公仔機好夾（唔識玩日式兩爪嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7360c7de2ba742a893d08c1949d851f5cc81ff","tid":994974,"uid":34295,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死打手<br />\n你篇文假撚到仆街"},{"pid":"c4d8306dc151fafebb065cd1cc8f6a005a958342","tid":994974,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a7360c7de2ba742a893d08c1949d851f5cc81ff","tid":994974,"uid":34295,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死打手<br />\n你篇文假撚到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"有時坦坦白白認好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b85ea4708b01ef2c8ee843d5149a426fe9f21ea","tid":994974,"uid":1557,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c4d8306dc151fafebb065cd1cc8f6a005a958342","tid":994974,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a7360c7de2ba742a893d08c1949d851f5cc81ff","tid":994974,"uid":34295,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死打手<br />\n你篇文假撚到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"有時坦坦白白認好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c